      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Four-legged supports, usually having pairs of legs in an A-shaped configuration with a crossbar; often used in pairs to support wood while being sawed or for other purposes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
